title: Sweet Home Sextuplets
overview: Courtney and Eric Waldrop, their three older boys and sextuplet babies are coming to TLC with new series Sweet Home Sextuplets. A tight-knit family living on a sheep farm in small town Alabama, parents Courtney and Eric got the surprise of their lives when trying for one more baby yielded sextuplets. In six, one-hour episodes, viewers are invited to join the family just before they give birth, through their high-risk delivery, the babies' admittance to the NICU and adjusting to a new normal after bringing them all home.
